Screen Edge Margins
Phone:   16dp left/right (screen_margin_horizontal)
Tablet:  24dp left/right (screen_margin_horizontal_large)
Foldable open: 24dp + respect hinge safe area

Typography System
All text uses Material 3 type scale. Never set font size, weight, or family manually.

Type Scale Reference
M3 Token	Style Resource	Usage
displayLarge	?attr/textAppearanceDisplayLarge	Hero text, marketing
displayMedium	?attr/textAppearanceDisplayMedium	Large emphasis text
displaySmall	?attr/textAppearanceDisplaySmall	Prominent text
headlineLarge	?attr/textAppearanceHeadlineLarge	Screen titles
headlineMedium	?attr/textAppearanceHeadlineMedium	Section headers
headlineSmall	?attr/textAppearanceHeadlineSmall	Sub-headers
titleLarge	?attr/textAppearanceTitleLarge	Toolbar titles
titleMedium	?attr/textAppearanceTitleMedium	List item titles
titleSmall	?attr/textAppearanceTitleSmall	Small labels
bodyLarge	?attr/textAppearanceBodyLarge	Primary body text
bodyMedium	?attr/textAppearanceBodyMedium	Secondary body text
bodySmall	?attr/textAppearanceBodySmall	Captions, hints
labelLarge	?attr/textAppearanceLabelLarge	Button labels
labelMedium	?attr/textAppearanceLabelMedium	Chip labels, tabs
labelSmall	?attr/textAppearanceLabelSmall	Overlines, badges
Usage in XML:

<TextView
    android:textAppearance="?attr/textAppearanceBodyLarge"
    ... />

✗  android:textSize="16sp"       — hardcoded, doesn't follow type scale
✗  android:textStyle="bold"      — hardcoded weight, breaks type system
✓  android:textAppearance="?attr/textAppearanceBodyLarge"

