Layout Quality Checklist
Run before marking any layout complete. Every box must be checked.

Structure
 Root layout uses CoordinatorLayout (for screens with toolbar) or ConstraintLayout
 View hierarchy depth ≤ 5 levels
 No nested LinearLayouts where ConstraintLayout eliminates them
 No android:layout_weight in LinearLayout inside ScrollView
Resources
 Zero hardcoded dimension values — all reference @dimen/
 Zero hardcoded color values — all reference ?attr/ or @color/ tokens
 Zero hardcoded strings — all reference @string/
 Zero hardcoded text sizes — all reference ?attr/textAppearance*
Material Design 3
 All interactive components use Material 3 widget classes (not plain Android widgets)
 Buttons use correct style variant (filled / outlined / text) for action priority
 Cards use MaterialCardView (not FrameLayout / CardView from androidx.cardview)
 Text inputs use TextInputLayout + TextInputEditText
States
 Loading state layout defined (shimmer or progress indicator)
 Empty state layout defined (illustration + message + action)
 Error state layout defined (message + retry button)
 Success state layout defined (primary content)
Responsiveness
 Layout tested at 360dp width (small phone)
 Layout tested at 411dp width (standard phone)
 Landscape variant exists or tested to not break
 Tablet variant exists for content screens (w600dp alternative)
Accessibility
 Every ImageView has contentDescription (or @null for decorative)
 All touch targets ≥ 48dp × 48dp
 All text uses sp units
 All layout_margin* and padding* use Start/End (not Left/Right)
 Contrast ratios meet 4.5:1 for body text (verify with accessibility scanner)
 Focus order is logical (top→bottom, start→end)
Dark Mode
 All colors use ?attr/ theme attributes
 No @color/white or @color/black for semantic elements
 Verified in both Light and Dark themes
RTL
 All directional attributes use Start/End
 Directional icons marked android:autoMirrored="true" where appropriate
Anti-Patterns Reference
Anti-Pattern	Why It Fails	Correct Approach
android:textSize="16sp"	Bypasses type scale, not globally changeable	android:textAppearance="?attr/textAppearanceBodyLarge"
android:textColor="#000000"	Breaks dark mode, not themeable	android:textColor="?attr/colorOnSurface"
android:background="@color/white"	Breaks dark mode	android:background="?attr/colorSurface"
Nested LinearLayouts 3+ deep	Exponential measure passes, slow rendering	ConstraintLayout with direct constraints
android:layout_weight inside ScrollView	Infinite height conflict, layout broken	Fixed dimensions or ConstraintLayout
match_parent height on RecyclerView inside ScrollView	RecyclerView cannot recycle, OOM	Use NestedScrollView + app:layout_behavior or fixed height
android:layout_marginLeft	Breaks RTL layouts	android:layout_marginStart
android:onClick="handleClick" in XML	Requires specific method name in host, untestable	Set listener in Fragment/Activity code
Missing loading/empty/error states	Blank screen confuses users	All four states defined in every screen layout
Icon as android:src PNG bitmap	Blurry on high-DPI, large APK	VectorDrawable with app:srcCompat
CardView from androidx.cardview	M2 component, no M3 token support	MaterialCardView from Material library
Plain Button or EditText	No Material theming applied	MaterialButton, TextInputLayout + TextInputEditText
Hardcoded android:hint="Enter email"	Not localizable	android:hint="@string/hint_email"
Missing contentDescription on icon buttons	TalkBack announces "unlabeled button"	Always provide meaningful contentDescription
Touch target below 48dp	Impossible to tap for users with motor difficulties	Enforce 48dp minimum via android:minWidth/Height or padding
